<plot>Vera, after her umpteenth fight with Gennaro, decides to seek elsewhere happiness. Giulio comes as a "Deus ex machina" and she does everything to conquer him, but he, with the first occasion, falls in love with Foglia. The latter soon leaves Giulio to seek love in the arms of Gennaro, prolonging this chain of incomplete relationships. Gennaro will close all this, creating an endless circle...or giving to Vera an another opportunity... will she manage to seize it?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?215467</url></doc>
